WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.760
Sharon McGrane is next, she is the author of highly praised books about scientific discoveries

00:07.760 --> 00:10.360
and the scientists who make them.

00:10.360 --> 00:15.360
She is interested in exploring the connection between social issues and scientific progress

00:15.360 --> 00:19.900
and in making the science clear and interesting to non-specialists.

00:19.900 --> 00:23.340
Her first book.

